[
    {
        "content": "<p>Hi, is there any reason to override <code>to_uniform_space</code> in <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/add_subgroup.seminormed_add_comm_group_quotient\">docs#add_subgroup.seminormed_add_comm_group_quotient</a> ?</p>",
        "id": 350897494,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1681857633
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Why not use the <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/find/add_group_seminorm.to_seminormed_add_group\">docs#add_group_seminorm.to_seminormed_add_group</a> constructor + default <code>uniform_space</code> instance coming from the norm?</p>",
        "id": 350897627,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1681857681
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It was backported from LTE in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib/pull/7603\">#7603</a> by <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"110031\">@Patrick Massot</span></p>",
        "id": 350898185,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1681857889
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The answer is provided in the <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib/blob/cd8fafa2fac98e1a67097e8a91ad9901cfde48af/src/analysis/normed/group/quotient.lean#L331-L335\">next five lines</a> of this file (and the module docstring). The complicated version ensures:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">add_subgroup</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">quotient.topological_space</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">topological_space</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span> <span class=\"bp\">â§¸</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span>\n<span class=\"n\">S.seminormed_add_comm_group_quotient.to_uniform_space.to_topological_space</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"n\">rfl</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 350902557,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1681859669
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You can delete the <code>to_uniform_space</code> and <code>uniformity_dist</code> field in that instance to see this <code>rfl</code> fail.</p>",
        "id": 350902645,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1681859712
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"face palm\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f926\" role=\"img\" title=\"face palm\">:face_palm:</span> I should've read this before asking.</p>",
